HEADWORD: Wealdish
<hw>Weald"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to a weald, esp.
to the weald in the county of Kent, England.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
